# Plan-and-Execute — REST Client (VS Code: REST Client by Huachao Mao)
# Run worker: npm run worker:plan-and-execute (from repo root)

@base = http://localhost:3000
@workflowId = <paste workflowId from start response>

### Start plan-and-execute agent (bus trip word problem)
POST {{base}}/agents/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentName": "planExecuteAgent",
  "input": {
    "message": "A school is organizing a trip. Each bus can carry 48 students. There are 376 students going on the trip. Each bus costs $325 to rent. The school also pays a flat parking fee of $180 for the entire trip. What is the total transportation cost for the trip?"
  } 
}

### Get run status
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}

### Get run result (wait until status is COMPLETED)
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}/result
